  <script>
    function showProposal() {
      document.getElementById('content').innerHTML = `
        <h1>Hano üíï</h1>
        <p>You are the most amazing person I‚Äôve ever met.<br>
        I love your personality, your smile, and everything about you. ü•∞<br>
